00:46:21.799 --> 00:46:25.930
on, you know, are you using an HSA or your
bus pass or whatever it might be.

00:46:25.930 --> 00:46:30.729
Basic bottom line I would say is, "Start off
with the simplest example you can, and then

00:46:30.729 --> 00:46:34.930
just deduct the taxes out of there.
In the grand scheme of things, it shouldn't

00:46:34.930 --> 00:46:38.680
